title: PUMA Women's Tazon 6 Sneaker
description: If your priorities look something like this: working out, eating, sleeping...We get it. And you'll get it when you lace up this new edition of our sleek tazon training shoes, engineered to give you a comfy and stable ride like none other. T-toe construction lace closure for a snug fit midfoot saddle for optimum fit and comfort Breathable ecoortholite sockliner for optimum fit and comfort cushioned midsole for comfort eva heel pod offers cushioning and shock absorption TPU shank for increased stability rubber outsole for grip PUMA Formstrip at lateral side.
